But when you start realizing the people I would talk to years ago that have followed this build don’t even get to see these posts really blows lol at the end of the day. It’s fun regardless of what we do. Either eating with the boys. Cruising or even posting once a week. Ig just needs to take it back to the old school way 😭😂

IMHO...if someone actually cares whether IG is “dry” or not, they take IG way way too seriously.  This is for fun.  A good way to meet people, communicate, share appreciation for cool shit, cool cars, cool places, good food, whatever you are passionate about.  But there is zero payoff for “content”. Just have fun with it!  I used to post like every day.  Now...maybe once a week.  The most of what I post is the famous #CheechBirthdayCards.  I hope people still enjoy them.  I only make them for people I know, people I respect and people who are actual friends.  I just have fun with IG.  Not in it for likes or followers.  Honestly, it’s awesome that you and I met many years ago, basically thru IG...and that we are still boys today, all these years later.  Thank you for that brotha! 🙌🏼😉
